<note resp="#resp1" n="0868004" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0868004">弟子【大】＊，佛說弟子【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note type="mod" resp="#resp1" n="0868005" target="#nkr_note_mod_0868005">笮【大】，作【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
